title: [FSX/P3D] OFX Simulation - Lisbon City Landmark 2014
description:
OFX Lisbon is a scenery representing major buildings and monuments of the capital of Portugal, one of the oldest city in the world. The scenery is fully adapted to Aerosoft Mega Airport Lisbon V2.0/V1.0. This scenery provide to simmers a more realistic approach and takeoff operations in Lisbon Portella airport.

Features :

Major buildings of Lisbon (especialy very important VFR such as : Vasco da Gama bridge, Cristo de Rei, etc...)
3D light for night scenery
Car animations
Bird animations
Boat in ports of Lisbon
Aerial imagery 50 cm (included Costa da Caparica beach)
Entire mesh of Portugal (16 m)
FPS Friendly
